{"tid":2313618,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國眾議院週一有望通過《香港人民自由和選擇法案》　為受迫害港人提供庇護","createTime":"2020-12-06T03:14:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T09:02:42.000Z","uid":35519,"like":67,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"4b25b775bd9a49df5d806aa7f1b6ef9cd2d09f33","tid":2313618,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T03:14:08.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">美國眾議院週一有望通過《香港人民自由和選擇法案》<br />\n為受迫害港人提供庇護</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gdb.voanews.com/7703315D-88CE-4AE4-850E-55C1B1A5A151_cx0_cy11_cw0_w1023_r1_s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgdb.voanews.com%2F7703315D-88CE-4AE4-850E-55C1B1A5A151_cx0_cy11_cw0_w1023_r1_s.jpg&h=084faa61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n延遲​兩個多月遲遲未出現進展的《香港人民自由與選擇法》（Hong Kong People's Freedom and Choice Act）在本屆國會議期結束前最後一刻獲得參眾兩院通過的希望出現曙光。<br />\n<br />\n根據國會議程安排，眾議院週一（12月7日）將就《香港人民自由與選擇法》進行全體院會審議表決。如果法案獲得眾議院通過，即可送交參議院等待投票，這將像徵法案在完成立法程序的道路上往前邁進一大步。法案在通過國會參眾兩院後，才得以遞交到白宮，由總統簽署生效。<br />\n<br />\n這項法案被列為&ldquo;擱置辯論規則&rdquo;(suspension)，即指法案不存在爭議，獲得至少三分之二議員的支持，立法過程進入快速通道，在全院的審議辯論限時40分鐘，內容上不會有新的修正案。也就是說，人們可以預期，法案將在美東時間星期一下午的投票中獲得通過。<br />\n<br />\n根據編號HR8428《香港人民自由與選擇法》，<strong><ins>美國政府將為目前已持簽證在美國，但返回香港可能面臨政治迫害的香港人提供&ldquo;臨時保護身份&rdquo;（Temporary Protected Status）。法案還將加速處理為逃離政治迫害的香港居民赴美難民申請程序，並將此類別申請排除在美國每年整體難民接收人數限制之外。</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n此外，<strong><ins>即使美國撤銷部分或全部香港的經貿特殊地位待遇，法案將在移民政策類別上將香港有別於中國大陸的移民申請。法案同時將推動國際合作，特別是鼓勵理念相近的盟國為受到北京壓迫的香港人提供庇護。</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n報道全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/us-house-to-vote-on-bill-to-provide-asylum-status-for-hong-kong-residents-20201205/5688971.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Fus-house-to-vote-on-bill-to-provide-asylum-status-for-hong-kong-residents-20201205%2F5688971.html&d=3iOM3afBfBP%2FWcaFgxWQo4%2FVxAEwmAwDimrVtn2syv4%3D&h=88d0188c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/us-house-to-vote-on-bill-to-provide-asylum-status-for-hong-kong-residents-20201205/5688971.html</a>"},{"pid":"9835a347645b1119219c702dc127d212134a7069","tid":2313618,"uid":253016,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T03:15:29.000Z","msg":"14億被迫害香港人要出現了"},{"pid":"75b884e22bddbaf25e85564e738ad69f9719f73f","tid":2313618,"uid":82394,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T03:15:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f77112454cd28d15ce5f69ae621dbaa05007ca","tid":2313618,"uid":51583,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T03:16:02.000Z","msg":"係希望有人跟既啫<br />\n普通人唔易成功"},{"pid":"5659d1703ccc042af686ddb7ebb338e93b1929cc","tid":2313618,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T03:16:35.000Z","msg":"拜登見到更加唔高興<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9c48e97f48d50fc1fdd00c9536e0b75ba255736","tid":2313618,"uid":35519,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T03:17:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Yanky_Pollak/status/1335406991695548419\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FYanky_Pollak%2Fstatus%2F1335406991695548419&d=3iOM3afBfBP%2FWcaFgxWQo4%2FVxAEwmAwDimrVtn2syv4%3D&h=62ae0e23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FYanky_Pollak%2Fstatus%2F1335406991695548419&h=a495ed4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Yanky_Pollak/status/1335406991695548419</a><br />\nWe will not bend. <br />\nWe will not break. <br />\nWe will not yield. <br />\nWe will never give in.<br />\nWe will never give up.<